        <h2 class="post-list-heading"><a href="https://www.hendrik-erz.de/post/electron-chokidar-and-native-nodejs-modules-a-horror-story-from-integration-hell">Electron, chokidar, and native Node.js modules: A horror story from integration hell</a></h2>
        <div class="post-list-metadata">
            November 5th, 2022 | by Hendrik
        </div>
    
        <p class="post-abstract">
            Today I want to tell you a story that starts in February of 2018 and haunted me until this very day. It is a story about the failure of both myself and the largest software company on earth, Microsoft, to solve a very obscure problem for four years.
        </p>
